that will generate each sequence.

Sequence                                        Expression
a. 2, 4, 6, 8, 10, 12, ...                      2 * count
b. 4, 19, 34, 49, 64, 79, ...                   15 * count - 11
c. 30, 20, 10, 0, -10, -20, ...                 -10 * count + 40
d. -7, -3, 1, 5, 9, 13, ...                     4 * count - 11
e. 97, 94, 91, 88, 85, 82, ...                  -3 * count + 100
